\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/e92e4b070aff5df42e927618f6b5175c.poster.avif?t=1731638463\" width=750 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/e92e4b070aff5df42e927618f6b5175c.webm?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/e92e4b070aff5df42e927618f6b5175c.mp4?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Your torch has an important place in Brink of Death.<br>And you need to make good use of your Resources.<br>And remember, you have plenty of safe places to hide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/a2bae12e9c7305813d4654491031788e.poster.avif?t=1731638463\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/a2bae12e9c7305813d4654491031788e.webm?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/a2bae12e9c7305813d4654491031788e.mp4?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/69a90a2f0169ca0ff38681d8fbcd919e.poster.avif?t=1731638463\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/69a90a2f0169ca0ff38681d8fbcd919e.webm?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179940/extras/69a90a2f0169ca0ff38681d8fbcd919e.mp4?t=1731638463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><b